---
title: Mighty Mushroom Tortilla Melts with Caramelized Onion & an Apple Salad
description: Move over, quesadillas. These days, we’re all about tortilla melts! In all seriousness, though, our newest obsession is really just a spin on its south-of-the-border cousin. Our tortilla melts are similarly golden and crispy on the outside and packed with flavor (and cheese). Inside, there are savory sauteed mushrooms and onions, plus cheddar and Monterey Jack. It all gets drizzled with lemony crema and served alongside an apple-studded salad. Prepare to melt!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6239d54bf2907366e348025e-dcccfcf9.jpg
